find yourself again. Pretty soon you break off the 
combat and it, and of course, the little

11:21.904 --> 11:34.456
commercial radios we had, sometimes you hear the 
boss, I mean the commander call in and say, okay,

11:21.904 --> 11:34.456
it's breaking off, go back. And sometimes you 
don't, you just do it on your own. And a lot of our

11:36.958 --> 11:42.844
combat was that way, where they'd just, we'd wait 
