When on the ground in the parking area, I found in my 
maven's eye a bullet hole in my right aileron,

13:02.827 --> 13:08.232
right stabilizer and rudder. I reflected back now 
about that quiver in my coat. I remember that. I

13:13.995 --> 13:16.938
remember this very day, all of a sudden, I felt it. 
Your airplane was quivering? Yeah, and the stick.

13:19.681 --> 13:20.222
Oh, I see. The rudder, the whole airplane. Boy, you 
